.TH SINGINE-INTRANET 1 "2026-03-22" "singine 0.2.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
singine-intranet \- generate local sindoc.local intranet control pages
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B singine intranet control-center
[\fB--output-dir\fR \fIPATH\fR]
[\fB--home-dir\fR \fIPATH\fR]
[\fB--dotfiles-repo\fR \fIPATH\fR]
[\fB--ai-root-dir\fR \fIPATH\fR]
[\fB--repo-ai-dir\fR \fIPATH\fR]
[\fB--json\fR]
.br
.B singine intranet publish
[\fB--site-root\fR \fIPATH\fR]
[\fB--deploy-root\fR \fIPATH\fR]
[\fB--silkpage-root\fR \fIPATH\fR]
[\fB--ssl-dir\fR \fIPATH\fR]
[\fB--domain\fR \fIDOMAIN\fR]
[\fB--no-sync\fR]
[\fB--json\fR]
.br
.B singine intranet cert-bootstrap
[\fB--ssl-dir\fR \fIPATH\fR]
[\fB--domain\fR \fIDOMAIN\fR]
[\fB--force\fR]
[\fB--json\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B singine intranet control-center
writes a unified local control-plane page under
.IR sindoc.local .
It brings together:
.IP \(bu 2
machine identity and repo root
.IP \(bu 2
dotfiles summary and link to the dotfiles control page
.IP \(bu 2
Claude and Codex session summary and link to the session dashboard
.IP \(bu 2
live Docker edge container status
.IP \(bu 2
command snippets for edge runtime actions
.PP
.B singine intranet publish
syncs the generated intranet into a Silkpage-style deploy root, writes a local
deployment dashboard under
.IR /deploy/ ,
and emits the matching Apache vhost, hosts fragment, and TLS readiness report
for
.IR sindoc.local .
It also writes a Firefox
.I policies.json
snippet that enables enterprise-root import.
.PP
.B singine intranet cert-bootstrap
creates a local root CA and a server certificate for
.IR sindoc.local
under
.IR ~/.config/lutino/ssl ,
so Apache has concrete TLS material to serve and Firefox can be pointed at a
real trust anchor instead of a missing certificate path.
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
singine intranet control-center \\
  --output-dir /Users/skh/ws/git/github/sindoc/singine/target/sindoc.local/control \\
  --json

singine intranet cert-bootstrap \\
  --ssl-dir /Users/skh/.config/lutino/ssl \\
  --json

singine intranet publish \\
  --site-root /Users/skh/ws/git/github/sindoc/singine/target/sindoc.local \\
  --deploy-root /Users/skh/var/deploy/sindoc.local \\
  --silkpage-root /Users/skh/ws/git/github/sindoc/silkpage \\
  --json

singine web /Users/skh/ws/git/github/sindoc/singine/target/sindoc.local --port 8080
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR singine (1),
.BR singine-ai (1),
.BR singine-dotfiles (1),
.BR singine-edge (1),
.BR singine-man (1)
